I added some buttons into a UIStackView but the image overlaps the button.

[gallery ids="1046,1047" type="rectangular"]

I modified the <em>contentEdgeInsets</em>
<pre>CGFloat inset = (self.frame.size.height - totalHeight)/2;
self.contentEdgeInsets = UIEdgeInsetsMake(inset, 0.0f, inset, 0.0f);</pre>
